    <h1>The Southern Company (SO)<br/>Intrinsic Value</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A transparent, two-stage discounted cash flow valuation of Southern Company. Using FY2025 actuals, disclosed assumptions, and generating a single fair value estimate.</p>
    <p class="date">Updated March 18, 2026 · Data: FY2025 10-K</p>
