  <h2>Sensitivity Analysis</h2>
  <p>Our base case uses 5% Phase 1 growth and a 7% discount rate. Here's how the intrinsic value changes if those assumptions vary.</p>

  <div class="table-wrap">
    <table class="sensitivity-table">
      <thead>
